hbase
=====

Install and configure the Apache HBase package from taball.


Filesystem layout
=================

/opt/hbase       -- symlink to the versioned installation directory /opt/hbase-1.x.x
/var/log/hbase   -- log directory for HBase and Zookeeper
/run/hbase       -- pid files
/var/zookeeper   -- ZooKeeper data directory


Jobs you need to do manually after running the playbook
=======================================================

# su hdfs
$ hdfs dfs -mkdir /hbase
$ hdfs dfs -chown hbase:hbase /hbase
$ exit
# su hbase
# start-hbase.sh


Role variables
==============

hbase_version
-------------

Version of HBase to download and install.
